Q. Can I wear Selenite Bracelet daily?

Yes, it can be worn daily for calmness, meditation, self-care, prayer, and peaceful energy support.

Q. Which wrist should I wear it on?

Wear it on the left wrist to receive calming, cleansing, and healing energy.

Q. Is Selenite self-cleansing?

Yes, Selenite is traditionally known as a self-cleansing crystal and is also used to refresh the energy of nearby crystals.

Q. Who can wear this bracelet?

It is suitable for men and women who want peace, clarity, aura cleansing, and a meaningful healing bracelet.










